<br>
I'm seeking a more solid identity for every group.  Community within a community within another community.<br>
<br>
Race/city/continent - good, bad, neutral.<br>
<br>
What does it mean and what do we feel about one another.  We have many notorious players who are well known.  We know for the most part who they are.  But what do we really know about the Wood Elves, the Iksar, the Trolls, etc.? Who are they really?  Sony has already laid out the groundwork.  We need to bring it to life.<br>
<br>
Does anyone see where I'm going here? <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=driaann>DriaAnn</A> at: 10/10/03 10:45 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=driaann>DriaAnn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Don't Mess with the Mage!<br>
